 specifies the algorithm for averaging pixel intensities												- there are 12 algorithms available.  algorithms generally follow the form:red = (n1*((green+green_coef)+(blue+blue_coef)))*(n2*(red+red_coef));green = (n1*(red+red_coef)+(blue+blue_coef))*(n2*(green+green_coef));blue = (n1*(green+green_coef)+(red+red_coef))*(n2*(blue+blue_coef));												- the different variations determine the n1 and n2 coefficients to the algorithms and whether they are applied to all channels in the same way.